{"tid":2155071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城狗屋扯錯旗 妹仔區旗大過主人婆國旗","createTime":"2020-08-13T13:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T13:53:24.000Z","uid":321059,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0705d2f02597d9e6c133d6ced8e79bcc8a635e0a","tid":2155071,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=20f78c34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA%2F&h=42ea0f54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍城警署升旗出現「妹仔大過主人婆」現象，《蘋果》發現警署升掛起的國旗與區旗，區旗大過國旗，國旗亦相對褪色，傍晚所見仍未被糾正，《蘋果》正就事件向警方查詢，暫未回覆。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n政府總部禮賓處有更詳細說明，國旗與區旗同時或並列升掛、使用時，區旗應小於國旗，亦不得展示或使用破損、污損、褪色或不合規格的旗幟。有關內容同見於教育局「認識國旗、國歌與區旗」章節。<br />\n<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793aa845ff9ffb110ff5c7c6e993d7d1926a9b0f","tid":2155071,"uid":321059,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEOvAF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEOvAF4.jpg&h=6b262ec2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"065f109a267345065d78c51b1b6604074adc97c0","tid":2155071,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa